<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Differing from subsp. 
<taxonomicName authority="leichtlinii" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Lilium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Lilium leichtlinii subsp. leichtlinii" order="Liliales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="leichtlinii" subSpecies="leichtlinii">Lilium leichtlinii leichtlinii</taxonomicName>
in the following characters: 
<emphasis bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">bulb</emphasis>
with stolons that can extend to 
<quantity metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" unit="m" value="2.0">2 m</quantity>
; 
<emphasis bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">stem</emphasis>
green, purple streaked or spotted (vs. stem green unspotted); 
<emphasis bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">leaves</emphasis>
linear or lanceolate to 
<quantity metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.6" unit="cm" value="1.6">1.6 cm</quantity>
wide (vs. 
